M = I − X(X'X)^{−1}X'
A^2=A*A=A
M = I − X(X'X)^{−1}X'
M = XX' − X(X'X)^{−1}X'
MM = (XX' − X(X'X)^{−1}X')(XX' − X(X'X)^{−1}X')
MM = (XX' − X(X'X)^{−1}X')(I − I)
Tr(AB)=Tr(BA)
Tr(M)=Tr(I − X(X'X)^{−1}X') = Tr(I − I) = Tr(0) = 0
Tr(A-B)=Tr(A) - Tr(B)
Tr(M)=Tr(I) − Tr(X(X'X)^{−1}X')) = Tr(I) − Tr(I) = Tr(0)  or Tr(I)= Rank(n)
